1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 23=

4
00:00:36,359 --> 00:00:37,880
Xiaojiu.

5
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:39,679
Dasheng.

6
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:52,340
♪One thought pulls me in, the mortal
world becomes the battlefield♪

7
00:00:52,940 --> 00:00:58,300
♪Who traded true love
for a body covered in scars?♪

8
00:00:59,340 --> 00:01:05,980
♪The lanterns still burn,
but the vows have grown cold♪

9
00:01:06,420 --> 00:01:11,900
♪The road behind lies deep in snow,
but can't erase your warmth♪

10
00:01:12,740 --> 00:01:19,260
♪Someone gave their life
to keep one lantern bright♪

11
00:01:19,660 --> 00:01:25,700
♪It lit the barren road
and showed our last goodbye♪

12
00:01:26,300 --> 00:01:32,820
♪Someone still keeps a silent vigil♪

13
00:01:33,519 --> 00:01:34,519
(Peng Dasheng,)

14
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:39,200
(ever since I first saw you
on that flower carriage,)

15
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:41,840
(my heart has belonged to you.)

16
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:45,040
(But caught in the turmoil
of this mortal world,)

17
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:46,840
(I had no control over my fate.)

18
00:01:47,719 --> 00:01:49,560
(All I could do was leave
these feelings in a dream)

19
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,560
(and pretend we'd once been in love.)

20
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,920
(If fate ever lets us meet again,)

21
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,640
(I won't be such a coward.)

22
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,840
(The road ahead is long.)

23
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,920
(Take care of yourself.)

24
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:08,980
♪But this life we were given♪

25
00:02:10,060 --> 00:02:15,340
♪Can never be rewritten♪

26
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,080
Peng Dasheng.

27
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,039
Where's Su Yeye?

28
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,159
Peng Dasheng.

29
00:02:31,439 --> 00:02:32,439
Ms. Duan.

30
00:02:34,759 --> 00:02:35,960
Where did Su Yeye go?

31
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,520
I let her go yesterday.

32
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,360
You let her go?

33
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,520
She's one of those Demon Sect fiends.

34
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,719
And you just let her go?

35
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:47,479
She's just another poor soul

36
00:02:47,479 --> 00:02:49,199
the Demon Sect used.

37
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:50,120
Poor soul? Give me a break.

38
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,400
That temptress

39
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,960
has you under her spell.

40
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,560
Men really are all the same.

41
00:02:57,759 --> 00:02:58,240
Ms. Duan...

42
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,039
Don't explain.

43
00:02:59,159 --> 00:02:59,960
I don't want to hear it.

44
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,919
Who said I was going to explain?

45
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,240
I just wanted to know
why you're here so early.

46
00:03:08,759 --> 00:03:10,240
Murong Xiang sent for you.

47
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,400
He has something important to discuss.

48
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:21,240
Fellow martial artists,

49
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,000
our forces won a decisive victory

50
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:25,240
at Liuchu Manor.

51
00:03:25,319 --> 00:03:26,919
The Luocha Blade Demon was slain,

52
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:28,960
and the Demon Sect's remnants fled.

53
00:03:29,199 --> 00:03:31,240
This is a blessing
for the entire martial world.

54
00:03:33,159 --> 00:03:35,039
Amitabha.

55
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,039
Everyone,

56
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:38,000
I believe the Demon Sect

57
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:40,159
is now in decline.

58
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:43,240
We should press our advantage

59
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,560
and strike their stronghold.

60
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:45,680
We cannot give them

61
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:48,400
time to recover.

62
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:52,639
I've already ordered
Wudang's disciples to prepare.

63
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:54,199
Once Master Murong gives the word,

64
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:57,240
we can destroy their lair at Busi Sea.

65
00:03:57,439 --> 00:03:59,759
Destroy their lair at Busi Sea!

66
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:02,560
Destroy their lair at Busi Sea!

67
00:04:02,599 --> 00:04:06,719
Destroy their lair at Busi Sea!

68
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,199
No!

69
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:09,400
Destroy their lair at Busi Sea!

70
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:16,639
Elders,

71
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:19,800
the attack on Liuchu Manor
was only a ruse.

72
00:04:20,199 --> 00:04:21,120
Their real goal

73
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:23,560
was to make us lower our guard.

74
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:27,839
Mr. Peng, you made your name
fighting the Luocha Blade Demon.

75
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,639
Yet now you're
making the enemy sound invincible.

76
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:33,720
Are you afraid of Master Baiyi?

77
00:04:33,759 --> 00:04:34,519
Sir,

78
00:04:34,879 --> 00:04:36,839
I've fought Master Baiyi before.

79
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:38,439
His cultivation is unfathomable.

80
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,759
More importantly,

81
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:41,560
he knows everything that goes on

82
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,519
between our sects.

83
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:43,759
I suspect

84
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,319
he may be hiding

85
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,519
among us right now.

86
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,000
What?

87
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,439
How could that be?

88
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:55,639
Nonsense!

89
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:56,680
Many of us here

90
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:59,319
fought him years ago.

91
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,360
If he were among us,

92
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,000
wouldn't we recognize him?

93
00:05:03,319 --> 00:05:05,240
With war between good and evil
about to begin,

94
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,240
we must stand together

95
00:05:07,319 --> 00:05:08,399
against our common enemy.

96
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:11,240
Yet you're trying
to turn us against each other.

97
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,360
What's your real motive?

98
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,560
Amitabha.

99
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,560
Mr. Peng, as a hero's son,

100
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,639
you should know better
than to speak so recklessly.

101
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:23,000
Don't bring trouble on yourself.

102
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,120
To be honest,

103
00:05:24,639 --> 00:05:26,160
Master Baiyi told me that day

104
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:27,160
that he plans

105
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,639
to drain the life essence
of martial artists everywhere

106
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:31,199
and break through
the final barrier to godhood.

107
00:05:31,199 --> 00:05:32,600
If we rush in now,

108
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,519
we'll walk straight into his trap.

109
00:05:36,439 --> 00:05:37,560
Mr. Peng,

110
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:40,319
did that demon scare you
out of your wits?

111
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,160
If that were really his plan,

112
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,720
why would he tell you?

113
00:05:44,839 --> 00:05:46,759
It was only a bluff.

114
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:49,319
He was buying time

115
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:51,800
for the Demon Sect to recover.

116
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,720
At the Battle of Liuchu Manor,

117
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:56,439
every sect talked big,

118
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,439
then sent only the old,

119
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:59,800
the weak, and the wounded.

120
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:02,120
You were all waiting
for someone else to die

121
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,839
so you could claim the rewards.

122
00:06:04,639 --> 00:06:06,759
Now the Demon Sect is on the run,

123
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:09,040
and you're all racing
to take the credit.

124
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:13,439
And you call yourselves
respected elders and righteous leaders?

125
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:14,759
You're nothing

126
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:18,120
but hypocrites
looking out for yourselves.

127
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:18,800
Insolence!

128
00:06:19,279 --> 00:06:20,199
Duan Qingyao,

129
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:23,040
your master has only just passed.

130
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,800
That's the only reason
we've shown you any respect.

131
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,040
Say one more outrageous thing,

132
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:30,360
and I won't hold back.

133
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,639
Ms. Duan said

134
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,199
exactly what I wanted to say.

135
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,519
Believe us or don't.

136
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:38,319
We're leaving.

137
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,399
Wait.

138
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,839
What do you want?

139
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:46,240
Fellow martial artists,

140
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:49,639
there's something I need to clear up.

141
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,720
That day,
I took one look at the soul jade

142
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:56,800
and declared Peng Dasheng
to be Peng Zhen's son.

143
00:06:57,199 --> 00:06:59,040
Afterward, I realized

144
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:01,040
I'd been too hasty.

145
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,639
So I quietly had

146
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:05,399
Peng Dasheng's background investigated.

147
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,720
And sure enough,

148
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:09,399
I uncovered a few clues.

149
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:12,639
Guards,

150
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,439
bring her in.

151
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:22,959
Mr. Murong.

152
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:24,439
My respects.

153
00:07:24,439 --> 00:07:27,040
Tell everyone the truth.

154
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,600
I used to be a midwife
at the foot of Wuhu Mountain.

155
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,560
Twenty years ago,

156
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:33,240
I took in a baby boy

157
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:35,079
from a blacksmith's family.

158
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:37,360
A plague had struck their home.

159
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:39,759
His mother died shortly
after giving birth.

160
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:42,680
Before she died, she begged me
to save the baby.

161
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:47,240
Later, I found out
the boy was gravely ill.

162
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,319
No one would pay for him.

163
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,000
I...

164
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:52,920
I planned to abandon him
at the foot of Wuhu Mountain

165
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,199
and leave him to his fate.

166
00:07:54,319 --> 00:07:55,560
What are you trying to say?

167
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:58,240
On my way up the mountain,

168
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:01,439
I saw a warrior lying by the roadside.

169
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:04,600
A dead baby was strapped to his chest.

170
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:07,040
I panicked,

171
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:08,839
left the boy beside him, and ran.

172
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:10,680
Later, I heard

173
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:13,920
the leader of Wuhuduandao Sect
had adopted a baby boy

174
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:16,040
and named him Peng Dasheng.

175
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,439
I believe that boy

176
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:23,839
was the blacksmith's own son.

177
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,800
No... Wait...

178
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:35,080
So Peng Dasheng isn't

179
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:38,720
Mr. Peng Zhen's son?

180
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:39,320
He's...

181
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,759
He's just a blacksmith's son?

182
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:42,240
That's right.

183
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:43,200
Exactly.

184
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:43,919
Impossible!

185
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,840
My master told me

186
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:48,039
my father brought me
to the sect himself.

187
00:08:48,039 --> 00:08:49,120
My master wouldn't lie to me.

188
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,240
You may go.

189
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:51,960
Yes.

190
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,200
Peng Dasheng,

191
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:54,919
after all this,

192
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:56,919
are you still going
to cover for your master?

193
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:58,720
What do you mean?

194
00:08:58,919 --> 00:09:00,720
It's perfectly clear.

195
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:02,799
When your master arrived,

196
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,919
he found two bodies

197
00:09:05,159 --> 00:09:07,200
and a crying baby.

198
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:10,000
That baby was you, Peng Dasheng.

199
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:12,240
Your master took you in

200
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:14,600
and left you Mr. Peng Zhen's soul jade

201
00:09:14,879 --> 00:09:16,559
as proof of your identity.

202
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:18,639
If I'm not Mr. Peng Zhen's son,

203
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:21,200
why would my master
leave me his keepsake?

204
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,360
That was all part of your master's plan.

205
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:26,240
Wuhuduandao Sect was only a minor sect.

206
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,240
He wanted to use Mr. Peng Zhen's fame

207
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,840
to raise its standing.

208
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,519
You were an abandoned orphan

209
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,840
with no family or ties,

210
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,039
easy to control.

211
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:38,840
You were the perfect choice.

212
00:09:39,399 --> 00:09:40,559
Your master learned

213
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:42,919
that Mr. Peng Zhen and I
were sworn brothers

214
00:09:43,159 --> 00:09:45,200
and that I alone knew the secret.

215
00:09:45,399 --> 00:09:46,840
So he carefully arranged

216
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:49,440
your engagement to Bingqing.

217
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,440
He knew that at the martial tournament,

218
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:53,559
I'd recognize the soul jade on you.

219
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:55,440
Then he could use your name

220
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,720
to raise Wuhuduandao Sect's
standing again.

221
00:09:58,759 --> 00:09:59,559
Peng Dasheng,

222
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,639
from beginning to end,

223
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:04,159
you were nothing but a pawn
in your master's hands,

224
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,600
a puppet on a string.

225
00:10:16,799 --> 00:10:17,799
Fellow martial artists,

226
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:22,000
what use do we have for a man

227
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,960
who falsely claims to be a hero's son

228
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,200
and sows discord among us?

229
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:31,360
I propose that Peng Dasheng
be cast out of the martial world

230
00:10:31,919 --> 00:10:34,039
and forbidden from ever returning.

231
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:35,039
Banish him!

232
00:10:35,039 --> 00:10:35,840
Cast him out!

233
00:10:35,919 --> 00:10:36,519
Banish him!

234
00:10:36,519 --> 00:10:37,320
Cast him out!

235
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,440
Cast him out!

236
00:10:39,559 --> 00:10:40,320
Banish him!

237
00:10:40,519 --> 00:10:41,600
Cast him out!

238
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:43,440
Banish him!

239
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,720
I never belonged
to your martial world anyway.

240
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,159
All you ever argue over

241
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:50,360
is pedigree.

242
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,799
But since the day
I came down the mountain,

243
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,559
I never once tried

244
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:56,399
to live off Mr. Peng Zhen's name.

245
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,240
And I have no desire

246
00:10:59,120 --> 00:10:59,759
to stand beside

247
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:01,720
hypocritical elites like you.

248
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:02,879
Peng Dasheng,

249
00:11:03,159 --> 00:11:04,600
the martial world has its order

250
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,639
and its rules.

251
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:08,600
You don't get to defy them!

252
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:09,639
Rules?

253
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:12,159
The rules that made you stand by
while people died at Liuchu Manor?

254
00:11:12,759 --> 00:11:15,159
Or the rules that make my birth a crime?

255
00:11:16,519 --> 00:11:17,720
And you, Murong Xiang.

256
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:20,840
Why are you so eager to brand me guilty?

257
00:11:21,639 --> 00:11:22,440
Could it be

258
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,399
you're in league with the Demon Sect?

259
00:11:28,639 --> 00:11:29,960
Nonsense!

260
00:11:30,399 --> 00:11:31,200
Guards!

261
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,960
Throw this arrogant troublemaker out!

262
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:34,799
Don't bother.

263
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,240
Since you've made up your minds
to cast me out,

264
00:11:37,919 --> 00:11:40,639
I want no part
of this rotten martial world

265
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:41,960
that can't tell right from wrong.

266
00:11:43,519 --> 00:11:44,759
From this day on,

267
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:47,639
I will have nothing
to do with the martial world.

268
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:51,559
Whether you live or die
is no concern of mine.

269
00:11:53,159 --> 00:11:53,960
Let's go.

270
00:12:27,559 --> 00:12:28,919
Are you thinking about your master?

271
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,960
I never doubted him.

272
00:12:35,639 --> 00:12:37,759
Everything that old fox
Murong Xiang said

273
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:40,240
was just a power play.

274
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:42,120
Then is it your background
that's bothering you?

275
00:12:47,399 --> 00:12:48,639
Back on the mountain,

276
00:12:48,799 --> 00:12:51,399
Master never cared
where any of us came from.

277
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:53,320
But out here,

278
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:56,039
people rank you by birth.

279
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:02,039
I just don't understand.

280
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,559
When they said I was

281
00:13:03,559 --> 00:13:05,240
Mr. Peng Zhen's posthumous son,

282
00:13:05,559 --> 00:13:07,039
they made me commander of the alliance,

283
00:13:07,559 --> 00:13:09,240
as if I were born for greatness.

284
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,600
And now?

285
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:13,159
They call me a blacksmith's son,

286
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,639
and suddenly, I'm a fraud

287
00:13:14,639 --> 00:13:15,639
everyone turns against.

288
00:13:17,159 --> 00:13:18,480
Tell me, aren't the rules

289
00:13:18,639 --> 00:13:19,759
of the martial world a joke?

290
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:24,399
My master told me

291
00:13:24,559 --> 00:13:26,000
that in the old days,

292
00:13:26,039 --> 00:13:27,399
two martial artists could become friends

293
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:30,240
over a flask of wine.

294
00:13:33,639 --> 00:13:35,120
No one cared whether you came
from a famous martial family

295
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,360
or were a beggar off the street.

296
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,559
But now,

297
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:42,519
everyone treats pedigree
as the only thing that matters.

298
00:13:42,679 --> 00:13:43,759
They've got it all backward.

299
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,639
But about your background...

300
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,519
Do you really believe that midwife?

301
00:13:52,559 --> 00:13:54,360
It doesn't matter whether I believe her.

302
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,480
Even if I am

303
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:59,639
a blacksmith's son, so what?

304
00:13:59,919 --> 00:14:01,279
I'll still raise my blade

305
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:03,080
and cut through this unjust world.

306
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,639
Too bad

307
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:18,000
I'm already dying.

308
00:14:18,559 --> 00:14:22,039
I don't know if I'll live to see it.

309
00:14:25,039 --> 00:14:25,840
Peng Dasheng,

310
00:14:26,759 --> 00:14:28,399
I know you will.

311
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,360
You're the only person in this world

312
00:14:36,399 --> 00:14:37,840
who still believes in me.

313
00:14:52,639 --> 00:14:55,399
Master, the leaders and disciples
of Wudang, Emei, and the other sects

314
00:14:55,399 --> 00:14:56,440
are ready and waiting

315
00:14:56,519 --> 00:14:57,360
for your order.

316
00:14:57,559 --> 00:15:00,200
But Kongtong and several other sects
are still holding back.

317
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,759
They may have plans of their own.

318
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,440
Send my order.

319
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:06,240
Every sect leader

320
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:09,639
must personally lead their best fighters

321
00:15:09,759 --> 00:15:11,639
to Busi Sea tomorrow.

322
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:13,440
Anyone who refuses

323
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,879
will be treated
as a Demon Sect collaborator

324
00:15:15,279 --> 00:15:16,120
and executed without mercy.

325
00:15:16,679 --> 00:15:17,039
Yes.

326
00:15:45,159 --> 00:15:47,679
(Yehuo Honglian, Demon Sect)
Sacred Altar Guardian, Yehuo Honglian.

327
00:15:47,879 --> 00:15:48,720
(Yehuo Niepan, Demon Sect)
Yehuo Niepan.

328
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:50,720
We greet you, Master.

329
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:56,120
How goes the task I gave you?

330
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,200
Master,

331
00:15:57,399 --> 00:15:59,039
as ordered,

332
00:15:59,159 --> 00:16:01,240
we've recalled every Demon Sect disciple
scattered across the land

333
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:02,799
to Busi Sea.

334
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,799
At your command,

335
00:16:05,159 --> 00:16:06,559
we'll move out in full force.

336
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,320
Good.

337
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,840
In a matter of days,

338
00:16:13,039 --> 00:16:15,840
I'll break through
the final barrier to godhood

339
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:18,399
and rule over every martial artist
under heaven.

340
00:16:19,559 --> 00:16:21,759
Then the Demon Sect's name

341
00:16:22,039 --> 00:16:23,919
will shake the world,

342
00:16:24,039 --> 00:16:25,559
and all lands will bow before us.

343
00:16:25,799 --> 00:16:28,639
You two, return to Busi Sea at once.

344
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:30,320
Make sure nothing goes wrong.

345
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:31,759
As you command.

346
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:33,039
Master,

347
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:36,320
Peng Dasheng
is the Demon Sect's sworn enemy.

348
00:16:36,559 --> 00:16:38,519
With every major sect
gathering at Busi Sea,

349
00:16:38,799 --> 00:16:40,600
we can't let him leave alive.

350
00:16:42,399 --> 00:16:45,399
Don't worry. He'll come.

351
00:16:57,759 --> 00:16:58,200
Who's there?

352
00:17:17,260 --> 00:17:17,740
♪Come on♪

353
00:17:21,260 --> 00:17:22,940
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

354
00:17:24,900 --> 00:17:27,860
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

355
00:17:28,140 --> 00:17:31,060
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

356
00:17:31,300 --> 00:17:34,140
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

357
00:17:34,540 --> 00:17:37,140
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

358
00:17:37,660 --> 00:17:40,620
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

359
00:17:40,860 --> 00:17:43,860
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

360
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:46,940
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

361
00:17:47,100 --> 00:17:49,860
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

362
00:17:50,420 --> 00:17:53,740
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

363
00:17:53,780 --> 00:17:56,780
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

364
00:17:56,820 --> 00:18:02,460
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

365
00:18:02,860 --> 00:18:04,900
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

366
00:18:05,460 --> 00:18:07,980
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

367
00:18:08,700 --> 00:18:11,100
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

368
00:18:11,220 --> 00:18:14,900
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

369
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:17,620
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

370
00:18:18,540 --> 00:18:20,660
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

371
00:18:20,820 --> 00:18:24,100
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

372
00:18:24,140 --> 00:18:28,420
♪I am my own king♪

373
00:18:41,500 --> 00:18:43,060
♪I emerge into the world♪

374
00:18:43,060 --> 00:18:44,820
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

375
00:18:44,820 --> 00:18:46,180
♪My pride is my trump card♪

376
00:18:46,180 --> 00:18:47,980
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

377
00:18:47,980 --> 00:18:49,380
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

378
00:18:49,380 --> 00:18:51,140
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

379
00:18:51,140 --> 00:18:52,660
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

380
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:54,380
♪I dare to break every rule♪

381
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:55,700
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

382
00:18:55,700 --> 00:18:57,540
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

383
00:18:57,540 --> 00:18:58,780
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

384
00:18:58,780 --> 00:19:01,020
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

385
00:19:01,020 --> 00:19:02,540
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

386
00:19:02,540 --> 00:19:04,140
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

387
00:19:04,140 --> 00:19:05,740
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

388
00:19:05,740 --> 00:19:07,460
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

389
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:09,180
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

390
00:19:09,180 --> 00:19:10,540
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

391
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:12,180
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

392
00:19:12,180 --> 00:19:13,660
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

393
00:19:13,660 --> 00:19:15,380
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

394
00:19:15,380 --> 00:19:16,980
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

395
00:19:16,980 --> 00:19:18,540
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

396
00:19:18,540 --> 00:19:22,860
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

397
00:19:22,860 --> 00:19:25,020
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

398
00:19:25,020 --> 00:19:27,620
♪Let me write the legend♪

399
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:35,060
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

400
00:19:35,060 --> 00:19:38,380
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

401
00:19:38,380 --> 00:19:40,860
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

402
00:19:40,860 --> 00:19:44,940
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

403
00:19:45,300 --> 00:19:47,900
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

404
00:19:48,020 --> 00:19:50,380
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

405
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:53,420
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

406
00:19:53,420 --> 00:19:58,460
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
